view.name: CA Educational Attainment & Personal Income 2008-2014
view.description: California Educational Attainment & Personal Income as captured by the US Census Current Population Survey (CPS) for years 2008-2014.

Dataset Summary Section.Limitations/Exclusions: Use of this data is subject to the CA.gov Conditions of Use and any copyright and propietary notices incorporated in or accompanying the individual files

Narrative Information Section.Data Collection Methodology: The American Community Survey (ACS) is a national survey that uses continuous measurement methods. In this survey, a series of monthly samples produce annual estimates for the same small areas (census tracts and block groups) formerly surveyed via the decennial census long-form sample.
